This Default Job ID is to be used exclusively for transactions that fall under the Tag Caffe vertical with no specific Job to track them under. TAG Caffe Vertical relates mostly to service over counter to Taggers, Catering, and other campus food services.

This Default Job ID is to be used exclusively for transactions that fall under the Events vertical with no specific Job to track them under. Events refers to special production events that typically arrive from the B2B Channel. This Vertical Should not be confused with community events.

This Default Job ID is to be used exclusively for transactions that fall under the Subleasing vertical with no specific Job to track them under. Subleasing refers to campus space leased to parters within a campus. Typically with longer lease agreements and a portion of our building expenses.

This Default Job ID is to be used exclusively for transactions that fall under the Colearning vertical with no specific Job to track them under. Colearning are educational products launched within the campus space for members, they are independently managed from Learn BU.

This Default Job ID is to be used exclusively for transactions that fall under the Managed Contracts vertical with no specific Job to track them under. Managed Contracts are typically campuses for which we only have an operating management fee arrangement with low expense committment.

This Default Job ID is to be used exclusively for transactions that fall under the Sponsorships & Branding vertical with no specific Job to track them under. Sponsorship, Branding and Product placement fall unther this vertical. These services are typically B2B channel managed.
